after 10 am 
mccann said instruments recorded a 48 magnitude on the richter 
scale the epicenter was 120 miles southwest of san juan in the mona 
passage which divides puerto rico and hispaniola island 
puerto rico civil defense director heriberto acevedo said the 
agency had no reports of injury or damages 
mona passage is a high seismic zone registering some 2000 small 
tremors a year 
the richter scale is a measure of ground motion as recorded on 
seismographs 
an earthquake of 35 on the richter scale can cause slight damage 
in the local area 4 moderate damage 5 considerable damage 6 
severe damage 
