speech in taking on the new directions movement the biggest 
internal challenge a union administration has faced in 40 years 
to be frank i think those who say that workers dont want 
change in the workplace who insist that the old ways were always 
the best ways are insulting the intelligence of uaw members 
bieber said amid cheers from about 2000 convention delegates 
